snippet.title: The Chill Zone
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Chill Zone, a channel of pure fun. This is a love project of mine, that helps me relax , train my editing skill, and use this social midea platform, the way it was entended to. To learn, inspire and shitpost. 
-
Tuesday & Thursday -  usually a short format video about warhammer 40K 
Monday or Wednesday - Gaming and Social Media Rants
Friday (Saturday on odd occasions) - Absolute shit post, were i go off tangent and rant about suff i like. 

My inner repressed weeb wants to do some Anime related contant at some point, but that is to be continued  ( queue roundabout  by Yes)
